Package: okeanos.nbp.interface
Type: Package
Title: This package implements querying National Bank of Poland's API from R
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Artur Wegrzyn
Maintainer: Artur Wegrzyn <awegrzyn17@gmail.com>
Description: This package contains functions for querying the API of National 
    Bank of Poland for FX rates (cf. http://api.nbp.pl/en.html).
    The available FX rates are the FX rates agains Polish zloty. The available 
    Available FX rate pairs against zloty are:  AUD, THB, BRL, BGN, CAD, CLP, 
    CZK, DKK, EUR, HUF, HKD, UAH, ISK, INR, HRK, MYR, MXN, NZD, NOK, PHP, GBP, 
    ZAR, RON, IDR, RUB, SGD, SEK, CHF, TRY, USD, KRW, JPY, CNY.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
